    "ArticleTitle": "Role of capsule and suilysin in mucosal infection of complement-deficient mice with Streptococcus suis.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "2460",
      "EndPage": "2471",
      "MedlinePgn": "2460-71"
